text: Dietikon is the fifth largest city of the canton of Zurich in Switzerland, after Zürich, Winterthur, Uster and Dübendorf. It is the capital of the same- named district of Dietikon. ==Gallery== File:Dietikon - Bremgartenstrasse IMG 6137 ShiftN.jpg|Bremgartenstrasse in Dietikon and St. Agatha Kirche in the background File:Dietikon - Limmattal - Grunschen IMG 6124.JPG|Dietikon as seen from Grunschen and Limmattal in the background File:BahnhofDietikon1.JPG|Dietikon train station File:BDWM BDe 8-8 Ortsdurchfahrt Dietikon.jpg|S17 line provided by the Bremgarten-Dietikon-Bahn File:Dietikon - St. Agatha Kirche IMG 6141 ShiftN.jpg|St. Agatha Kirche ==References== ==Other websites== * Official Website of the city of Dietikon * Category:Municipalities in Dietikon Category:Cities in Switzerland
